Detailed Description

Contains an interpreted data message. The class provides easy access to the contained data through its many functions.

A pointer to an XsDataPacket object.

See also
C Interface For the C interface Global functions.

The data items contained in XsDataPacket other will be added to this packet. Items that are already present will be overwritten depending on the value of overwrite.

Parameters
otherThe XsDataPacket to read the data items from
overwriteWhen set to true, existing items will be overwritten, otherwise they will not be modified
Returns
Returns the updated data packet
